			<div class="comment" style="word-break:keep-all; white-space:nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow:ellipsis; position: absolute; top: 70%; left: 110%; opacity: 0.2;"><h2><p style="text-shadow: 1px 1px 1px #bbb;">Enjoy it!</p></h2>
			</div>
		<% } %>
		<p>12. If you have any idea to share with me, please email me at pc30@rice.edu.</p>

	</div>
</div>

